{"tid":1321691,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［閱兵］721晚上民陣集會，展示最強之矛最強之盾，核子噴射器","createTime":"2019-07-15T17:40:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T01:46:52.000Z","uid":9049,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c4e32f2aa52cffe8532d1c5bbae9a898dc4dc8f6","tid":1321691,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T17:40:02.000Z","msg":"就係原子筆同memo紙啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n下面有文宣攻略/勇武攻略<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n廣告對白<br />\n<br />\n學生：對唔住，香港手發作！<br />\n<br />\n男老師：哼！用原子筆啦！<br />\n<br />\n女旁白：原子筆核子噴射器，對香港手確有功效。<br />\n<br />\n男旁白：喺月黑風高殺蟲夜，memo紙忍者為民除害，唔駛用劍嘅，用memo紙就得啦！<br />\n<br />\n女旁白：memo紙夠晒威，memo紙的確好使！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">文宣攻略：</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n721夜晚7點半到9點集會<br />\n<br />\n咁日頭咁長時間做乜好呢？<br />\n<br />\n唔好曬左佢，齊齊做文宣<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>港島處處連儂牆</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n文宣威力強大，文宣自己友圍爐冇意思<br />\n一定要比更多人知香港真實的一面<br />\n宣傳方面要勁過TVB<br />\n<br />\n@<br />\n我個藍絲老豆轉死性<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1321032\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1321032</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n@<br />\n<br />\n準備工作：<br />\nMemo 紙 大量<br />\n各種「噴射器」 愈多愈好<br />\n大透明膠紙 一人一卷<br />\n膠水AA膠各種膠 有幾膠要幾膠<br />\n長輩圖 一人十張<br />\n<br />\n最大風險：罰錢了事，不會被捕<br />\n<br />\n目標：目光所見，全部都係連儂牆<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">勇武攻略：</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n人一定多，幾萬人就迫爆政總啦，散要時間，一定話你非法集結，然後圍堵，包圍，大規模打人拉人<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>公民責任，拘捕冒警暴徒</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n集會人數迫爆就散去附近行下粘下memo紙<br />\n<br />\n當警方開始暴動、失控時，我地就要盡公民責任-拘捕暴徒<br />\n<br />\n第一步：附近民眾返金鐘，搞冒警暴徒後面，前後包抄，反包圍<br />\n<br />\n第二步：用索膠帶制服暴徒，唔好比佢傷人<br />\n<br />\n第三步：救自己人，粘memo紙落暴徒身上<br />\n<br />\n第四步：重複第一步<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n水炮車（水坦克）：見到就要走，極危險⚠️<br />\n<br />\n注意：國際規則：不打冇戰鬥力嘅人<br />\n<br />\n防線係死嘅，人先係生嘅。<br />\n<br />\n拘捕暴徒，人人有責<br />\n<br />\n不集結，周圍粘<br />\n<br />\nBe water"},{"pid":"9d5af1ad2c8735910ff451cff9ddda84cf0e2218","tid":1321691,"uid":95102,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T17:40:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">唔好意思阻你少少位<br />\n我打咗份聲明俾721嘅義士宣讀<br />\n希望各位巴打可以入嚟幫手改下</div></span><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n=========================<br />\n<br />\n721衝之前應該要搵人開記者會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1320570\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1320570</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n========================="},{"pid":"1f1d5f0f08fdd7953ffe2bccc973ddeefbd0c156","tid":1321691,"uid":238051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T17:40:29.000Z","msg":"【我冇嘢講2.0】<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>有人冒警！</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1319116\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1319116</a><br />\n<br />\n推post時幫手廣傳有人冒警！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>被動變主動</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">有人冒警！\n你扮警察\n涉嫌冒警及傷人\n涉嫌藏有攻擊性武器\n我地行使公民逮捕權</code></pre>"},{"pid":"065c291ac3ff9550128a07470c1e31903e3dabd8","tid":1321691,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T17:44:35.000Z","msg":"[突發]食環署就連儂牆發聲明<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1321578\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1321578</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n食環都唔理我地連儂牆，大家放心文宣<br />\n<br />\n文宣組好幸苦，我地幫輕下佢地好冇？"},{"pid":"3ae107aa5a2c1cc4cf3e3d8e066a0b426742766f","tid":1321691,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T01:19:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0d6909d94ca2f0eddc100a15680158bfdf043fcb","tid":1321691,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T01:46:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}